description: Had felt a weird strain in my right leg calf/achilles that kinda led into my shin near the end of my last couple runs - just stretched it out extra after but I could feel it right from the first stride this morning. Wanted to push through but inevitably had to stop. Everything aches, throbs for awhile & feels super tight - putting any pressure on it makes it hurt way more. Anyone with tips on stretching for this/technique advice please help a brother out!
